### Register
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "first_name": "Test",
  "last_name": "User"
}

### Login
# @name login
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/health

### Create Space
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/spaces
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

{
  "name": "My Study Group"
}

### Get My Spaces
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/spaces
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

### Send Message
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/spaces/{{spaceId}}/messages
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

{
  "content": "Hello everyone!"
}

### Get Messages
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/spaces/{{spaceId}}/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}
